      <h3>Why the Order Matters</h3>
      <p>Most performance brands talk about fitness as the top priority. Ascend does not. We put faith first - not as a religious statement, but as a performance principle. When your identity is rooted in something unshakeable, your training has a foundation that trends, injuries, and losses cannot erode.</p>
