      <h3>The Recovery Industry Has a Problem</h3>
      <p>Billions are spent on recovery products and protocols every year. Much of it is based on anecdote, social media preference, or marketing - not research. Here is what the evidence actually says about the most popular methods.</p>
      <h3>Sleep: The Only Non-Negotiable</h3>
      <p>No supplement, protocol, or technology replaces sleep. Studies consistently show that athletes sleeping less than 7 hours per night experience measurably reduced strength, slower reaction times, higher injury rates, and impaired muscle protein synthesis. Before spending a dollar on anything else, fix your sleep.</p>
